{"tid":2115684,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇肺炎康復者入黎分享下後遺症對生活影響","createTime":"2020-07-19T16:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T05:14:46.000Z","uid":33420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9d57563b9e90514ad15736874579e8465f1e6d","tid":2115684,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"雖然近呢個星期確診數目飇升<br />\n但其實過去半年都有好多康復者出左院<br />\n有啲甚至係後生 (例如exchange撚嗰啲）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>醫管局傳染病中心醫務總監曾德賢接受傳媒訪問時透露，目前正評估康復者的後遺症，現時有半數人換氣量不及常人8成，部分康復者更跌至常人3成半，可能與肺氣泡受病毒破壞相關。他形容康復者「平時坐着沒甚麼，但上斜路、行樓梯就感到吃力」。</em><br />\n<br />\n新聞雖然有咁寫<br />\n但外國甚至本地有人出院後仲可以繼續重訓運<br />\n跑步踢波籃球等等<br />\n真係想知道究竟出院後肺功能真係弱左好多？<br />\n後遺症對生活有咩影響？<br />\n可以如常生活以至扑野？"},{"pid":"71cb8950709ae44a04871e78b42d15ec80f28269","tid":2115684,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce465e078ce00bfd9f8a8e0fc16548ef93d9686b","tid":2115684,"uid":137927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b1fbace8dced6b3d12f8d6195205a5b004f4a8fe","tid":2115684,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"冇人想知？"},{"pid":"273703eed651ac14fb93aba78fa51bdc1cb738cf","tid":2115684,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"條J大碌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ab5939bf51ca3b78c0f997ba2ae8a706e97509","tid":2115684,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"想知<br />\n有冇Post discharge evaluation 既journal <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9888e9496af554f545fb32b09642612f3533d7cc","tid":2115684,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273703eed651ac14fb93aba78fa51bdc1cb738cf","tid":2115684,"uid":